1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,600
I've neglected it till now, but if they're anywhere, then it'd be up there.

2
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:07,240
I've tried listening, nothing.

3
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:10,480
I know they hear me, so why not come down for me?

4
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,640
Should I be afraid?

5
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:13,920
I wonder why they're hiding up there.

6
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:15,360
Did they turn on the lights?

7
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:18,800
Are they the reason time is frozen yet accelerating?

8
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:20,880
Are they why it's dark outside?

9
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:23,120
Am I really believing myself?

10
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:27,520
I haven't laid eyes on these things, yet I'm acting as if I'd better them.

11
00:00:27,520 --> 00:00:32,640
Maybe I am delusional, maybe this whole thing has been just delaying the inevitable.

12
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:35,760
Maybe I've completely lost my ever-loving mind.

13
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:40,800
I tried making food, but everything in my fridge was either spoiled, moldy, or growing something

14
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:41,800
unrecognizable.
